Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.45,0:00:04.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFF&\bord4}Rigor mortis...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:08.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFF&\bord4}It begins several hours after death,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:11.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFF&\bord4}and spreads to cover the whole body after about twelve hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.89,0:00:17.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFF&\bord4}But the spread of rigor mortis is also affected by the surroundings,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:24.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFF&\bord4}and may even be sped up depending on\Nthe victim's actions at the time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:26.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFF&\bord4}And as for those actions...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:31.77,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We won't give in to the hot blazing sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.77,0:00:33.48,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A gallant and dashing deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:36.65,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}With irreplaceable friends as suspects,\Nthe old man puts on his own deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.65,0:00:38.23,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:40.19,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:43.37,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
